      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a solid project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great chance to get into something inexpensive with plenty of potential. Ideal for a handy buyer, commuter backup, or someone who wants a budget-friendly car without spending a fortune. Priced fairly and offered by a straightforward seller who\u2019s happy to answer questions.",
